Manhole concrete module processing equipment Zhengzhou well wall block equipment introduction:
Zhengzhou Yixin is a professional manufacturer of concrete manhole block machines, manhole block machinery and wall block machinery. The company has semi-automatic to fully automated production lines.
Through years of practice and development, we have a high quality, mainly producing hydraulic, mobile, fully automated manhole series equipment and supporting devices.
Manhole concrete module processing equipment assembly site in Zhengzhou:
Manhole concrete module processing equipment. Features and advantages of Zhengzhou well wall block equipment:
Yixin manhole block machine is widely used in new type building materials of municipal underground structures, such as coal, heat, water, electricity, gas, etc.
Such as: inspection wells for drainage and water storage facilities, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks and small structures, wing walls of bridges, etc.
The advantage of using concrete blocks to build manholes is that the blocks have concave-convex slots on all sides, which interlock with each other when they are combined.
The shear strength of shaft wall is far better than that of plain friction masonry.
The module is a hollow structure. After combined building, the longitudinal holes are connected and the transverse holes are intersected. After pouring the hole core, it forms a cast-in-place concrete net structure, which plays a role of secondary reinforcement and waterproofing.
The module is provided with both transverse and longitudinal tie bars to improve the overall strength of structure.
In addition, the manhole and drainage well built by using concrete manhole block are not prone to collapse, sinkage and leakage. The wall block has stable mechanical properties, simple operation and standard forming size.
The intelligent control of concrete manhole block machine is equipped with data input and output device to monitor the whole process of mechanical operation by one key touch LCD display, realizing ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis ratio material, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
The mechanical and hydraulic system of the borehole wall module adopts single cylinder hydraulics and double cylinder hydraulics.
Independent hydraulic integrated station, avoiding the influence of host vibration on hydraulic system, thus ensuring the reliability of hydraulic system.
The feeding box of the block machine for concrete manhole rises with the traveling box, and the door of the storage box closes. The automatic conveying pallet is all independently completed by the hydraulic system, so as to reduce the wear and maintenance of the machinery.
The equipment adopts imported computers and electrical appliances, and hydraulic seals, which ensures the stability and reliability of the comprehensive performance of the equipment.
The mechanical vibration platform of the borehole wall module adopts a integral plate steel. The table is wire-cut with no welding points, which makes the stuffing box swing freely and guide, fully reducing mechanical wear.
Reduce the load of the mold, fillers and combine the amplitude of encryption, adopt integrated, full synchronization, table vibration, mold vibration to ensure the compaction effect.
The mechanical vibration machinery of the well wall module is automatically controlled by computer to adjust the amplitude according to the cost performance of raw materials, and has no wear braking, thus extending the service life and reducing the cost.
Double function of mechanical automatic control and manual control for wellbore wall module.
