In fact, there are many points for overweight girls to pay attention to when dressing.
A girl who is fat should wear a dress that is neither too short nor too long. It should be about knee-length, just to cover the fat part of her thighs.
A too short skirt will show off the fat on your legs.
A man who is too long will look short and fat.
If you wear different colors for the top, skirt and stockings, it will make you look taller.
In fact, many dark colors are the standard for overweight girls (the author has a deep feeling about this), and dark colors are also a good way to cover your body fat, and elegant black skirts are also the first choice for overweight girls.
Dark colors, especially black skirts, make you look slimmer.
If your calves are thick, don't wear socks and shoes that draw attention to them.
The more popular, the better, and don't use too bright colors.
So that people don't get the impression that you're fat because of your legs and feet.
For slightly overweight girls, it's important to teach them the tricks of dressing.
A girl who is a little overweight should not wear tight skirts, and her tops should not be too short or tucked in. If she has thick legs, she should wear black stockings or mesh stockings (fine mesh). She should also choose a soft printed bell-bottom skirt and a scoop-necked top to hide her shortcomings.
Of course, a chubby girl should be careful when wearing a short skirt.
If you are a chubby girl and wear a short skirt, you should choose a top with the same color as the short skirt, which will make your body look taller.
Short skirts with high heels can make your legs look longer, this is the most fashionable matching in summer!
If you are a chubby girl with thin legs, you can choose a gorgeous one-piece skirt.
It can not only cover your belly, but also show your advantage.
A-line skirts will slim you down, and are perfect for chubby girls. Pick a tight-fitting top to create a layered look that helps slim your figure.
A simple white T-shirt and a skirt, even a chubby girl can try this.
A girl with a little weight can also look fashionable.
As long as you can master the rules of dressing, overweight girls will be the focus of attention.
After the change in my dressing style, I need to exercise more in my daily life, so I can get rid of being overweight girl one day soon!
