Color classification: chip 1, chip 2, chip 3, chip 4, chip 5, chip 6, chip 7, chip 8, double chip
Thank you very much for choosing our product. Please take the time to read through this material before using our chips:
Please check that the goods are complete after unpacking.
Please contact customer service promptly if there is any omission.
The chip has a PC material cover plate. Do not use solvents that reacts with PC.
Do not inject directly into the chip with a syringe, as leakage may occur.
All chips with regular substrates are tested with pure water at injection pressure of 500mbar (for 100um channel depth) or 300mbar (for 50um channel depth) before shipment.
All glass chips are tested with pure water at 800mbar (100um channel) before shipment. Please be careful not to collide with sharp objects while using the chip, or the base may be damaged.
Use in combination with solution viscosity and do not exceed this range, otherwise leakage may occur.
For microfluidic chip with ordinary substrate, we suggest that the flow rate should be set below 150ul/min when using pure water for injection pump and below 50ul/min when using oil phase.
Please increase your flow rate from slow to fast depending on the viscosity of the actual injected liquid.
After the experiment with general purpose chips is completed, clean the inner channels promptly to avoid blockage.
The chip is consumable and cannot be reused for a long time.
No refund if the chip is damaged due to long-term use or improper operation.
If you need a microfluidic chip that can withstand higher pressure or flow rates, please contact us for customization.
Normal delivery cycle is within 1 week, in-stock parts can be shipped within 24 hours after ordering, please consult with our customer service before ordering.
If you have questions about how to connect our chip with your liquid sampling system, you can follow the link https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60474873 or search for “Mesoscopic Bio” for more help.
