At first was a friend's recommendation, trust him so I decided to have a look. At first my budget was 70k for basic decoration.
Started a little deception in the shop.
I have never been to this store before. They just looked at my layout plan and gave me a quote without measuring the house. They said that they can do it for 70,000 RMB for a 135 square meter house. They showed me some materials but didn't tell me what brand they are.
The second con is that once you arrive at the shop you will be pressured to pay a deposit (which you can never get back unless you have the experience to argue with them).
When I hesitated to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell you how much discount you can get if you pay the deposit today.
I am a victim of this big pitfall. I have paid more than 10,000 yuan for a house which was not available.
His quote to me had a lot of issues 70k not including plumbing or electrical, not including any doors and cabinets for the bathroom, and these three items are the biggest part of the base cost.
Their call charges are higher than those of other companies, except for their own services.
I lost my trust in this company. They ask me to sign the contract without explaining anything.
When I went to get my money back they were very experienced, a whole team of them came at me.
They would insist that it was the customer's own fault.
